# dinofyi — Python API Client Demo
Output demo.gif

Set FontSize 20
Set Width 1000
Set Height 580
Set Shell "zsh"
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 30ms
Set Padding 24

Type "uv run --with 'dinofyi[api]' python3"
Enter
Sleep 2.5s

Type "from dinofyi.api import DinoFYI"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "client = DinoFYI()"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "# Search dinofyi.com"
Enter
Sleep 0.5s

Type "client.search('tyrannosaurus')"
Enter
Sleep 2.5s

Type "exit()"
Enter
Sleep 1s
